5 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Transfer of funds. THE state treasurer shall transfer:
6 (1) $50 million from the general fund to the Montana water development state special revenue
7 account established in [section 1] by August 1, 2025; and
8 (2) $50 million from the general fund to the Montana water development state special revenue
9 account established in [section 1] by August 1, 2026.
10
11 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Codification instruction. [Section 1] is intended to be codified as an
12 integral part of Title 85, chapter 1, part 3, and the provisions of Title 85, chapter 1, part 3, apply to [section 1].
13
14 NEW SECTION. Section 6. Effective date. [This act] is effective on passage and approval.
